author: More Perfect Union
description:
Multiple companies don’t want you to know that they’re making money from Alligator Alcatraz.

Granny’s Alliance Holdings, IRG Global Emergency Management, CDR Companies, Gothams LLC, are collectively making millions — money coming from taxpayers.

These companies and their owners got these contracts after donating millions to the Trump machine and the Republican Party of Florida.
title: The Companies Making Money Off of Alligator Alcatraz
